subject: resource/NetSuite
object: NetSuite Inc. is an American software company based in San Mateo, California, that sells a group of software services used to manage a business's operations and customer relations. Customers access these services over the internet paying a periodic subscription fee. NetSuite's services are primarily aimed at medium- to enterprise-sized businesses.
